column5: Looking for some info on pine falls water temp and current is it still fast
Bill, water temp on Traverse Bay is 61.5F, current has dropped from the torrent it was a month ago but is still noticeable even out on the Bay. Congrats on your Red Lake finish.
thanks for the info got lucky in red lake caught the right ones

Heading up to Pine Falls Sept 19 for a week. Just testing the waters but feel confident. High water flow, reports of large amounts of bait fish in system and cooler than normal water temps for this time of year are pointing towards an early migration. I will report as the week goes on providing "Big Windy" allows it.
I look forward to your reports Mr. Elie.
